{"tid":1242253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[選民登記懶人包] 所有人入黎要佢血債票償！","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T08:09:26.000Z","uid":261180,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7e75119c3a90cda325c5499e27979f960f53dc86","tid":1242253,"uid":261180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4604o6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4604o6.png&h=b989887b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3PRrCr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3PRrCr.png&h=9cffdaad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/19/114332_a256558b5c78b23ec8574a0fdb9a5ee6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F114332_a256558b5c78b23ec8574a0fdb9a5ee6.png&h=6bd4452e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/19/114332_eb4484933ea2102ef60e6f082003eb3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F114332_eb4484933ea2102ef60e6f082003eb3f.png&h=8040a9ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/19/114333_7d287448e2ed1c82f1cc51f49a268c73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F114333_7d287448e2ed1c82f1cc51f49a268c73.png&h=42bcdf83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/19/114333_2083ac7d8886dd624487c666bc481fdd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F114333_2083ac7d8886dd624487c666bc481fdd.png&h=f6a99c14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/19/114334_3053a4c15e378c70239fbb32211e0dca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F114334_3053a4c15e378c70239fbb32211e0dca.png&h=f7fdf6c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4951596a2940d7237af5a0f4e721528bddacea8c","tid":1242253,"uid":261180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"上面個懶人包麻煩大家spread開！<br />\n登記左既都要check番！"},{"pid":"d9aaef9f3f9462555cac4beca6483c28ebde1be1","tid":1242253,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88bdc7b639652d5e5718d6386cce753cab58bb9","tid":1242253,"uid":258944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:48:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"10808384a6f41ddb1d3bc53af4d1a88a6747a19b","tid":1242253,"uid":258944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:48:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a71447cd093e950ebd02771615628e7bdcd009b1","tid":1242253,"uid":258944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:48:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"829a697394bcc2986d1ca9098447b9304cb6e436","tid":1242253,"uid":258944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:48:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a76316d933f544093e9039d276207bbc4b8c0bf1","tid":1242253,"uid":258944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:49:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"613670d3a198a5509478237b7d133665889b69c8","tid":1242253,"uid":261180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:49:11.000Z","msg":"血債票償！"},{"pid":"07307dc0bbb1b124d55a90aa889ededef9fec3d2","tid":1242253,"uid":258944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"519badfe510bc660642da50a4a5477f9cac84133","tid":1242253,"uid":258944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"20d695f23c0db683af620b603576c5a312a4e235","tid":1242253,"uid":258944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:49:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bf6c4aa927a9a7b4e488389173dc98d0db84660d","tid":1242253,"uid":261180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply